\nVM Consultants\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nHome  \\u00bb News  \\u00bb Supplier & Service Provider  \\u00bb Immersive LED feel at Unilumin's new experience centre\\n\\n\\nImmersive LED feel at Unilumin's new experience centre\\n\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t By Sakshi Sanghavi |\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tJuly 11, 2024\\nUnilumin\\u00a0has just opened its first state-of-the-art experience centre in Noida, which showcases the latest LED COB and MIP technologies and products with an immersive visual experience.\\n\\u00a0\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\nThe market for LED technologies and solutions is a promising one as brands across categories increasingly seek immersive ways of engaging their customers.\\u00a0\\n\\nUnilumin\\u00a0recently announced the opening of its first state-of-the-art Experience Centre in India at Noida, Uttar Pradesh. \\u201cThe centre represents a significant milestone in Unilumin\\u2019s expansion strategy, emphasising its commitment to the Indian market, with plans to establish additional centres across the country,\\u201d said the company statement.\\n\\nThe soft launch event was an exclusive gathering, inviting select partners and customers to witness Unilumin\\u2019s cutting-edge LED technologies. The experience centre offers an immersive visual experience, showcasing the latest LED COB and MIP technologies and products. Among the highlights were Micro LEDs, Transparent LEDs, and All-in-One displays, demonstrating applications in various settings such as control rooms, meeting rooms, XR studios, home cinemas, retail environments, education, and digital out-of-home (DOOH) advertising.\\n\\nApproximately 50 leading partners attended the event, engaging in in-depth exploration of the showcased products and interacting with the Unilumin team. This provided a platform for meaningful discussions and feedback, fostering strong relationships and collaborations. The attendees had the opportunity to experience first-hand the quality and capabilities of Unilumin\\u2019s LED solutions, which are designed to enhance visual experiences across various applications.\\n\\nVineet Mahajan, Director of India Business,\\u00a0Unilumin,\\u00a0commented, \\u201cThis state-of-the-art Experience Centre is dedicated to our partners and customers, aiming to raise awareness about the immense potential of LED displays. It will also serve as a learning centre for system integrator partners, where we will conduct regular training sessions on Active LEDs.\\u201d\\n\\nHe added that \\u201cThe LED display market is on an exponential growth at a CAGR of 28% YoY. This experience centre will help envisage the creative solutions.\\u201d\\nIn addition to the Experience Centre, Unilumin has established a fully equipped service centre on-site, enhancing their support capabilities and ensuring a superior customer experience. \\n\\u00a0 \\n\\nTags :\\nUnilumin\\nNoida\\nLED COB\\nMIP technologies\\nMicro LEDs\\nTransparent LEDs\\nExperience Centre\\nVineet Mahajan\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nAdvertisement\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\nPlease enable JavaScript to view the comments powered by Disqus.\\n\\n\\nRelated News\\n\\n\\n\\nEpson Certifies 3 StickyPOS liner-free media for OmniLink TM-L100 Thermal Label printer\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nPanasonic Life Solutions India launches fully integrated digital tent card display system\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nNew AI tool to help retailers with improved efficiency & customer experience\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nNext Articles \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nSunfeast YiPPee! ramps up the flavour at Puri Rath Yatra\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nMINISO opens Zanmang Loopy IP-themed store at Singapore\\u2019s Jewel Changi Airport\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nImmersive feel of products at Asian Granito\\u2019s new gallery in Ahmedabad Airport\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nAdvertisement\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nSubscribe to Our Newslette