-US\"\n        },\n        \"page_content\": \"\\n\\n\\n  \\n\\nLAVA Blaze X with Dimesity 6300 SoC, 6.67 inch 120Hz Curved AMOLED Display, Launched; Price Starts at INR 14999 \\u2022 TechVorm\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nFacebook\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nInstagram\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nTwitter\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nYoutube\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nApps\\nPhones\\nAppliances\\nAutomobile\\nBusiness\\nComputing\\nElectronics\\nReviews\\nVideos\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nSearch\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nTechVorm\\n\\n\\nApps\\nPhones\\nAppliances\\nAutomobile\\nBusiness\\nComputing\\nElectronics\\nReviews\\nVideos\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nHomePhonesLAVA Blaze X with Dimesity 6300 SoC, 6.67 inch 120Hz Curved AMOLED...\\nLAVA Blaze X with Dimesity 6300 SoC, 6.67 inch 120Hz Curved AMOLED Display, Launched; Price Starts at INR 14999\\n\\n\\n\\nBy Tech Desk\\n\\nJuly 10, 2024 \\n\\n0\\n\\n\\n\\nLava International HAS announceD expansion of its Blaze series with the launch of Lava Blaze X. It has a premium moonstone matte back design with Elegant Deco and comes in two color variants of Starlight Purple and Titanium Grey. It will be available on Lava e-store and Amazon starting 20th July.\\n\\n\\nThis smartphone flaunts a 6.67\\u201d 120 Hz Curved AMOLED Display(1080 X 2400 )with punch hole design. For imaging this phone id equipped with a 64MP + 2MP rear camera featuring the Sony sensor and a 16MP front camera. The camera offers several shooting modes including Dual View Video, Film, Pro Video, Slow Motion, Timelapse, UHD, Gif, Beauty, HDR, Night, Portrait, AI, Pro, Panorama, Filters, Macro, AI Emoji.\\u00a0\\n\\n\\nThis phone is powered by MediaTek Dimensity 6300 processor and is paired with three RAM options \\u20134GB+4GB virtual RAM, 6GB+6GB virtual RAM, and 8GB+8GB virtual RAM and128GB UFS 2.2 storage to enable smooth multitasking. Blaze X is packed with 5000mAh battery along Type C port and 33W Fast charging.\\nBlaze X comes with Lava promise of bloatware-free, ad-free experience and clean Android 14. Lava will offer regular software updates, including assured upgrade to Android 15, along with quarterly security updates for two years.\\nThis phone has in-display fingerprint sensor and offers connectivity options of 5G, Dual 4G, Wi-Fi, GPS, USB Type-C etc.\\nPrices and Launch offer Details:\\n\\n\\nLava will be offering Free Service @Home for Blaze X users, pan India alongside attending user concerns at Lava retail outlets.\\n\\nTopicsLAVA Blaze XLAVA International\\n\\n\\n\\nFacebookTwitterPinterestWhatsApp\\n\\n\\n\\nPrevious articleOnePlus Summer Launch Event \\u2013 Reveal of More Details of Products To Be LaunchedNext articleRealme Announces Offers on realme NARZO 70 5G starting from INR 13,999\\n\\nRELATED ARTICLES\\n\\n\\n\\nPhones  \\n\\nitel ColorPro 5G with MTK Dimensity 6080 Processor,Launched at INR 9999\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nPhones  \\n\\nOnePlus Nord 4 with Snapdragon 7+ Gen 3 SoC Announced; Price Starts at INR 29999\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nPhones  \\n\\nOnePlus Nord 4 and OnePlus Pad 2 will Come With AI Features\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nPhones  \\n\\nUpcoming HONOR 200 Series will Be Packed with 5200mAh 2nd Gen Silicon-carbon Battery\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nPhones  \\n\\nrealme 13 Pro Series 5G To Launch in India on July 30\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nPhones  \\n\\nUpcoming OnePlus Nord 4 Will Remain Cool Under High Temperatures as Claimed by OnePlus\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\nLEAVE A REPLY\\n\\n\\nComment:\\nPlease enter your comment!\\n\\n\\nName:*\\nPlease enter your name here\\n\\n\\n\\nEmail:*\\nYou have entered an incorrect email address!\\nPlease enter your email address here\\n\\n\\n\\