ednesday, July 17, 2024\\n\\nE-Paper\\nFeedback\\nContact Us\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nPragativadi | Odisha News, Breaking News Odisha, Latest Odisha News - Pragativadi | Odisha News, Breaking News Odisha, Latest Odisha News\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nHeadlines\\nState\\n\\nCrime\\nHuman Interest\\n\\n\\nTwin city\\n\\nBhubaneswar\\nCuttack\\n\\n\\nNational\\nInternational\\nBusiness\\nSports\\nE- paper\\nLifestyle & Culture\\n\\nTravel\\nHeritage\\nTourism\\n\\n\\nScience & Technology\\n\\nGadgets\\nMobile and Phones\\n\\n\\nEDITORIAL\\nBlog\\nEntertainment\\n\\nOllywood\\nBollywood\\nHollywood\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\nHomeScience & TechnologyLAVA Blaze X With Curved AMOLED Display Launched In India \\u0399 Check Specifications, Price\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\nLAVA Blaze X 5G\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nScience & TechnologyMobile and Phones \\nLAVA Blaze X With Curved AMOLED Display Launched In India \\u0399 Check Specifications, Price\\n\\n\\n\\nBy Yajati Keshari Rout \\nOn Jul 11, 2024\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Share\\n\\nFacebookTwitterTelegramWhatsapp \\n\\nBhubaneswar: Lava International Ltd., the leading homegrown Smartphone and wearable brand, announces the expansion of its Blaze series with the launch of its latest offering, the all-new Lava Blaze X.\\nSetting new benchmarks in the affordable smartphone segment, the Blaze X comes with the segment\\u2019s first Curved AMOLED display.\\nMr Sumit Singh, Product Head, of Lava International Ltd., said:\\n\\nLava Blaze has been one of our successful series which is conceptualised to address the industry gap with quality and powerful smartphones. The new Blaze X, the latest addition to the line-up is developed with three key parameters at the epicentre\\u2013 segment \\u2013 first curved Amoled display, performance and aesthetics. I hope the fans like our new Blaze X and enjoy the experiences that it is designed to deliver.\\n\\nLAVA Blaze X: Key Features\\n\\nThe smartphone flaunts a stunning 16.94 cm (6.67\\u201d) 120 Hz Curved AMOLED Display with a punch-hole design providing an immersive experience to the users.\\nPacked with a premium moonstone matte back design with Elegant Deco the new Blaze X exudes style and is a true trendsetter in the category.\\nEquipped with a 64MP + 2MP rear camera featuring the Sony sensor and a 16MP front camera, the new smartphone offers several shooting modes including Dual View Video, Film, Pro Video, Slow Motion, Timelapse, UHD, GIF, Beauty, HDR, Night, Portrait, AI, Pro, Panorama, Filters, Macro, AI Emoji.\\nDelivering an enhanced experience and superlative speed the smartphone brings the latest MediaTek Dimensity 6300 processor with AnTuTu 420K+, paired with three RAM options \\u2013 4GB+4GB*, 6GB+6GB*, and 8GB+8GB* boasting a generous 128GB UFS 2.2 storage to enable smooth multitasking and ample space for storage.\\nBlaze X comes with a 5000mAh battery along Type C port and 33W Fast charging.\\n\\nLava Blaze X price in India\\nThe price of Lava Blaze X in India has been set at Rs. 14,999 for the 4GB RAM + 128GB storage model. The 6GB and 8GB variants with 128GB storage are priced at Rs. 15,999 and Rs. 16,999, respectively.\\nAvailability:\\nThe new Blaze X comes in two stunning color variants Starlight Purple and Titanium Grey. It will be available on Lava e-store and Amazon starting 20th July.\\nContinue Reading \\n\\n\\naffordable smartphoneCurved AMOLED Displaylatest smartphoneLatest smartphones in Indialava blaze xLava International \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nYajati Keshari Rout\\n2408 posts\\n0 comments\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Prev Post\\t\\t\\t\\t\\nNEET-UG paper leak scam: CBI arrests mastermind Rakesh Ranjan\\n\\n\\nNext Post \\nOdisha C&T Dept Inks MoU With Navis HR to Create Overseas Job Opportunity for Skilled Drivers\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nYou might also like\\n\\n\\nMore from author\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\